data.description: Solid investment or owner occupied 3-unit in Saco. Each unit has been updated over the past several years. The building includes 7 heatpumps in all in two of the units. Parking for up to 5 plus vehicles, a spacious and private yard all within close proximity to downtown. Rare opportunity to own a property that will allow one to enjoy income investment potential, or in-law living opportunities. This 3-unit property has benefited from several recently completed renovations & improvements the last 10 years. Some of which include a New appliances, New flooring, New decks, Added Mini splits(Heat pumps). A total of 3,735 +/-sf of living space. For investment owners this property offers excellent rental income potential. Tenants will enjoy two spacious 2 bedroom units with hardwood floors, and one unit with 3 bedrooms and two full baths. Easy walk to Downtown Saco nd Biddeford and all it has to offer.  Easy access to Turnpike and Train Station. Expenses...Oil $1,600. CMP $3,100. Water/Sewer $953. Taxes 2021-2022 $8,006.54
